# Workflow Rerun From Snapshot

- When re-testing an existing workflow like `wf-XXXX`, use the run's own `config_snapshot.yaml` with `uv run python -m src.main run --config <run_dir>/config_snapshot.yaml --fresh`.
- Do not copy old YAML back into `config/review.yaml` just to rerun a past workflow.
- Use `resume` only to continue the same workflow. Use `run --config ... --fresh` to rerun old inputs after code changes.
- If you need live frontend logs, start or continue the rerun through the API-managed path, not a local-only CLI run.
- After making substantial changes based on a specific workflow, rerun it this way before claiming the fix worked.
